reviewText: My expectation as fully met.  Outstanding delivery.  Thank you soooo much.

if you don't like to cry, don't buy this. The acting is 1st rate, the actors more than pleasant to watch, and the story line is riviting. I'm not saying you can't figure out what comes next but you willingly suspend your knowledge just to be entranced in the action. My #1 favorite actor slot now has dual spaces! Guys, take my advise and be willing to watch it with your #1!
